  "remarks": "Pursuant to paragraph 6 of Security Council Resolution 2371 (2017), paragraph 6 of Security Council Resolution 2375 (2017)and paragraph 12 of Security Council resolution 2321 (2016). DPRK oil tanker M/V YU JONG 2 was involved in-ship-to ship transfer operations for oil in November 2017. M/V YU JONG 2 was also involved in a ship-to-ship transfer operation, likely for oil, with M/V MIN NING DE YOU 078 on 16 February 2018. Listed as asset of Korea Yujong Shipping Co Ltd (OFSI ID: 13637, UN Reference Number: UN Ref KPe.066)",
